data: {"type": "text-delta", "id": "edc1c0cb-9028-4264-b069-ebd291d4b812", "delta": "To check if a systemd service is active on RHEL 9:\n\n*   **Quick check (script-friendly):**  \n    `systemctl is-active <service_name>`  \n    Returns `active`, `inactive`, or `failed`.\n\n*   **Detailed status:**  \n    `systemctl status <service_name>`  \n    Shows active state, recent logs, and process info.\n\n*   **Check if enabled at boot:**  \n    `systemctl is-enabled <service_name>`"}

