data: {"type": "text-delta", "id": "d8c3cd53-66ee-46c2-b5d7-672809ed184c", "delta": "To check if a systemd service is active on RHEL 9:\n\n*   **Quick status check (script-friendly):**\n    `systemctl is-active <service_name>`\n    *Returns `active`, `inactive`, or `failed`.*\n\n*   **Detailed status:**\n    `systemctl status <service_name>`\n    *Shows active state, recent logs, and process details.*\n\n*   **Check if enabled at boot:**\n    `systemctl is-enabled <service_name>`"}

